<h2>What JavaScript can do?</h2>
<p>JavaScript cann change the HTML content.</p>
<button onclick="document.getElementById('my image').src='pic_bulbon.jpg'">Turn on light</button>
<img id="my image" src='pic_bulboff.jpg' style="width:200px">
<button onclick="document.getElementById('my image').src='pic_bulboff.jpg'">Turn off  light</button>
